offset.$description: value that is added on top of border-radius, i.e.: radius.sm + offset

scaling.$description: value that scales border-radius linearly, i.e.: radius.sm * scaling

offset.$description: value that is added on top of blur tokens in category dimension, i.e.: blur.sm + offset

scaling.$description: value that scales blur tokens in category dimension linearly, i.e.: blur.sm * scaling

offset.$description: value that is added on top of breakpoint tokens in category dimension, i.e.: breakpoint.lg + offset

scaling.$description: value that scales breakpoint tokens in category dimension linearly, i.e.: breakpoint.lg * scaling

offset.$description: value that is added on top of container tokens in category dimension, i.e.: container.5xl + offset

scaling.$description: value that scales container tokens in category dimension linearly, i.e.: container.5xl * scaling

offset.$description: value that is added on top of leading/line-height, i.e.: leading.02 + offset

scaling.$description: value that scales reference leading/line-height, i.e.: leading.02 * scaling

offset.$description: value that is added on top of font-size, i.e.: text-base + offset

scaling.$description: value that scales font-size linearly, i.e.: text-base * scaling

offset.$description: value that is added on top of font-weight, i.e.: font-weight-light + offset

scaling.$description: value that scales font-weight linearly, i.e.: font-weight-light * scaling

offset.$description: value that is added on top of letter-spacing, i.e.: tracking-wider + offset

scaling.$description: value that scales letter-spacing linearly, i.e.: tracking-tight * scaling

offset.$description: value that is added on top of sizing/padding/margin, i.e.: scaling-03 + offset

scaling.$description: value that scales sizing/padding/margin linearly, i.e.: scaling-03 * scaling
